<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bike Repair Process</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background:#f4f4f4;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
}

header{
    background:#222;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.container{
    width:80%;
    margin:auto;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.step{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    border-left:8px solid #ff6600;
    box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition:0.3s;
}

.step:hover{
    transform:scale(1.02);
}

h2{
    color:#ff6600;
}

footer{
    background:#222;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
    margin-top:30px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>🏍 Bike Repair Process</h1>
<p>Complete Service Workflow</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 1: Customer Inspection</h2>
<p>Check customer complaints and inspect the bike for visible damage.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 2: Engine Diagnosis</h2>
<p>Inspect engine oil, spark plug, battery, and fuel system.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 3: Brake Check</h2>
<p>Check brake pads, brake oil, cables, and braking performance.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 4: Chain & Gear Service</h2>
<p>Clean and lubricate the chain and adjust gear settings.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 5: Tyre Inspection</h2>
<p>Check tyre pressure, punctures, tread depth, and wheel alignment.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 6: Electrical Check</h2>
<p>Test headlights, indicators, horn, battery, and wiring.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 7: Oil Change</h2>
<p>Replace engine oil and oil filter if required.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 8: Final Test Ride</h2>
<p>Perform a road test and ensure all systems work properly.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h2>Step 9: Delivery</h2>
<p>Clean the bike and hand it over to the customer with service details.</p>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Bike Repair Management System
</footer>

</body>
</html>
